-- Invesco's second-quarter profit jumps 35.5 percent
-- 
-- Thu Jul 31, 2014 07:43AM EDT
-- None



NEW YORK, July 31 (Reuters) - Invesco Ltd <IVZ.N>, which oversees the PowerShares line of exchange-traded funds, said on Thursday that its second-quarter profit rose 35.5 percent as strong markets boosted the company's assets under management.

